{
  "stem": "7684.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And many times, we had to-- later on, we had to lay down on the floor, and going up, and laying down on the floor, until we met a whip hitting us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was-- there was always punishment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had always some kind of a punishment for us after we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very dangerous to do anything wrong because were all Germans standing there, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, I tried to sabotage always.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- when I did it, I cut always everything up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Chaim say to me, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Selma, ?] you know how dangerous it was later on?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I just still did it, cutting-- What-- what did you do?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I cut up nice blouses with a scissor or anything that was nice that I could cut up, I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that the Germans didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I know later on, already that everything went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Right, now this--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very dangerous to do things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then we were on roll call, and we walked to camp one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we came in camp one, there was already a big fire burning from the people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it smelled from hair and bone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had-- I didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came in camp one, and all the Germans were standing there, the SS's.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a few people that had instruments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took that with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had to play for the Germans, the enjoyment from the first-- second-- you know, something against-- I hated it again that we had to dance and play music and the fire was burning.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he-- they told us to dance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to dance, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
